<br>
Some of the individual scenes were incredible though.  The highway chase was fantastic.  I found myself flinching as Trinity drove the motorcycle against traffic.  The &quot;ghost&quot; twins were very cool, albeit they served little purpose in the grand scheme of things.  I'd liked to have seen them used for something more.  <br>
<br>
Overall I thought it was just ok.  There were some great individual scenes, but I didn't feel like it all tied together as well as the first one.  And I'm not even one of these fanatics about the first movie, I thought it was just a good movie.  This one was a good visual showcase, and an ok movie.  <br>
<br>
But, I may very well go back to see it on the Imax screens for that very fact. <p>-Tain<BR>
